desc_long								关于这款游戏							Welcome to Early Access of Shakedown Racing One! This product is not finished! Get it if you're excited to play in the current state.Colorful track racing on three locations with nine cars to choose from.CarsTuner, muscle, SUV, exotic type of cars each with its own character - rear, front and 4x4 cars. They will bite you, especially on jumps and corners. TracksTwisty tracks with many obstacles and challenges. It's fun, but prepare to be tested.ArenasNew game mode. The Stadium Arena may be close to a popular e-sport game, but it actually originates from a mode initially introduced in Ultimate Truck Simulator called "Balls and Gates". Balls, Gates, Colors in a sport event.GraphicsI usually steer to more realistic visuals, yet I've really come to love how this one turned out in the game. Mills, castles, ships, metal balls and pumpkins.Have fun!Head on to the discussion board for comments and suggestions.NOTE for Controllers: Menus are NOT supported, only cars. You can see the mappings here:https://www.flickr.com/photos/47251476@N05/26527195353/sizes/If you still want to change them you can go to the input tab on the game's launcher.https://www.facebook.com/sentinentialhttps://twitter.com/Sentinentialhttps://plus.google.com/+Sentinential						
